00:00:17.669 --> 00:00:19.460
be on the list of things
that are discussed

00:00:19.460 --> 00:00:20.620
with their teenagers.

00:00:20.620 --> 00:00:22.820
Recently, the massive
Snapchat hacking,

00:00:22.820 --> 00:00:25.580
which exposed personal
data of most of its users,

00:00:25.580 --> 00:00:28.580
got a lot of people talking
about sexting and privacy.

00:00:28.580 --> 00:00:30.150
