00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:31.530
published a new
study which found

00:00:31.530 --> 00:00:35.180
that 20% of seventh
graders are sexting.

00:00:35.180 --> 00:00:36.970
Now before your
jaw drops too far,

00:00:36.970 --> 00:00:38.720
the study sample
was seventh graders

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:41.130
who were identified by
their school counselor

00:00:41.130 --> 00:00:44.240
as already having some emotional
or behavioral difficulties.

00:00:44.240 --> 00:00:46.750
And of those in the study group,
those who were sexting were

00:00:46.750 --> 00:00:50.870
more likely to make out and
have sex than those who didn't.

00:00:50.870 --> 00:00:51.440
Shocker.

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:51.760
I know.

