Just so we're all
on the same page,

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:56.730
legally sexting refers
to sexual photo, video,

00:00:56.730 --> 00:00:59.120
and text messages sent
using a cell phone.

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:02.190
The National Campaign found
that across the board about 40%

00:01:02.190 --> 00:01:04.822
of teens have sent sexually
suggestive messages.

00:01:04.822 --> 00:01:07.280
A quarter of high schoolers
and a third of college students

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:09.850
admit to having sent and
received nude pictures.

00:01:09.850 --> 00:01:12.640
Sending text sex was more
common amongst young men,

00:01:12.640 --> 00:01:15.140
while sending nude
or semi-nude photos

00:01:15.140 --> 00:01:16.610
was more common amongst women.

00:01:16.610 --> 00:01:18.160
And 61% of the
women said that they

00:01:18.160 --> 00:01:19.920
felt pressured to
send the pictures.

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:21.980
So this makes me
wonder, why is sexting

00:01:21.980 --> 00:01:24.180
so common amongst teens?

00:01:24.180 --> 00:01:26.060
It's unfortunate that
a huge part of it

00:01:26.060 --> 00:01:27.650
